Detailed explanation of field contents:

A - The main number for the BBS, with area code.
  ex: 401-555-1234                                              Max width: 12

B - The complete name of your BBS system.
  ex: The Little Rhody BBS                                      Max Width: 21

C - Month and year that this BBS was put online. (continuous, with same name)
  ex: 07/95                                                     Max Width: 5

D - Online storage capacity of system in megabytes(mb) or gigabytes(gb).
    (includes magnetic hard disk space & mounted CD drive(s) only)
  ex: 210mb or 1.2gb                                            Max Width: 5

E - Number of RI lines/nodes/modems currently offered.
    (not including local nodes, telnet nodes, or call forwarded numbers)
  ex: 2                                                         Max Width: 4

F - The location of the BBS.
    (Rhode Island assumed)
  ex: E Providence                                              Max Width: 12

G - System Operator(s)
  ex: Joe Q. SysOp or John Doe/Jane Doe                         Max Width: 21

H - BBS software
    (Please do not include version numbers)
  ex: Wildcat                                                   Max Width: 9

I - Number of archives stored in local file library.
    (approximate - with comma, NO plus[+] signs)
  ex: 12,500                                                    Max Width: 7

J - Number of conferences/SIGS/message areas locally available on BBS.
    (approximate - with comma, NO plus[+] signs)
  ex: 38                                                        Max Width: 4

K - Additional information/feature field.
    (We suggest modem protocol, offline reader, special dialing instructions,)
    (CD, CB, theme/attraction of system, etc PLEASE USE A COMMA AND SPACE.   )
       *24/7 operation, Doors, Files, & baud speed # are not necessary*
  ex: v.32b, QWK, CD, model railroading enthusiasts             Max Width: 63

L - Number of doors/external programs online.
    (including games, utilities, mail doors, etc)
    (approximate - with comma, NO plus[+] signs)
  ex: 12                                                        Max Width: 4

M - Network offerings/affiliations.
    (includes all locally stored networks & links to live services. Please)
    (separate each entry with a comma and space.  If NONE leave *BLANK*.  )
  ex: Fidonet, Syndicate Net, RIME, Fishnet, Internet Mail
      or
      Fidonet, Internet FTP/GOPHER/MAIL/TELNET                  Max Width: N/A


